    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain the ability to reap life energy from creatures you kill with your spells. Once per turn when you kill one or more creatures with a spell cast using a spell slot, you gain Temporary Hit Points equal to twice the slot level, or three times its level if the spell belongs to the School of Necromancy. You do not gain this benefit for killing Constructs or Undead.</p><p>When you reach level 10 in Wizard, if you have no more than half your Hit Point maximum then you can regain Hit Points rather than Temporary Hit Points if you choose.</p>",
